    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classopentelemetry_1_1sdk_1_1logs_1_1LoggerConfig" kindref="compound">LoggerConfig</ref> defines various configurable aspects of a Logger&apos;s behavior. This class should not be used directly to configure a Logger&apos;s behavior, instead a ScopeConfigurator should be used to compute the desired <ref refid="classopentelemetry_1_1sdk_1_1logs_1_1LoggerConfig" kindref="compound">LoggerConfig</ref> which can then be used to configure a Logger. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
